data.description: This beautiful single family dwelling/duplex home has high ceilings, high white cabinets, granite counter tops, a huge walk in shower, unique study space, and walk in closets in both the master and second bedroom. The home features an open concept with the living room and kitchen space. The exterior of the home features a large balcony space on the second floor that measures 26 X 7'8" and an enclosed gate with a high fence around the property. Please verify all room dimension information.
